fields.description:
Hi, I woul like to know what happened with this CH.

Elizabeth Sandoval Mendoza cproxy9760840417263

*+15096308405* WHATSAPP as method of notifications.

She called us because she receive her notifications, the only one she is not receiving is SALDO.

We did a test during our call:

She was able to receive a response for MOVIMIENTOS, but not for command 1. 

!image-20230623-041037.png|width=1213,height=363!



Can you please assist?

TIA!

comments.body:
[~accountid:642b1df702931fca47bde0c5]  not sure what’s goin on. I see that the {{1}} was coming in, and I also see in Twilio that the message got sent out.  I created a loom video so you can see how I did the troubleshooting.  {{https://loom.com/share/4a7e4b85953b45fabeb5b300e0560fe3?sid=bac6c903-ad09-4ff4-8479-cd80b2fe96fb}}

if {{1}} doesn’t work would {{BAL}} work instead?  Not sure if there’s a difference since I see that twilio did indeed send the message.
I don’t see any further actions for us at this point.

Hello [~accountid:613e6eaa1238e8007108f513] thank you for the video. Just to understand, we can see that messages are delivering without problems from our side and this should be related to an error from the CH side, correct?

[~accountid:636e6ef3c87c50433009887b] 
Maybe. We have delivered it and anything after we have delivered it is out of our hands. 
Maybe it was a whatsapp issue? We can’t see their systems and we can’t debug it further. 
Messages can also be delayed. There can be data connection glitches etc. 

My suggestion is to use keywords again if there’s no response.
Thank you [~accountid:613e6eaa1238e8007108f513] we will call her and try it again!
[~accountid:636e6ef3c87c50433009887b]  please let me know if it works. If it doesn’t work again then I am going to open up a ticket with Remitly to have them investigate it on their end

Hello [~accountid:613e6eaa1238e8007108f513] we called her but she didn’t respond our calls. Our process is that after 3 failed calls we close the ticket until they call us back so we might have to wait until she calls us again. Thank you for your assistance!

[~accountid:642b1df702931fca47bde0c5] 

I heard back from Twilio. They would like us to reach out to the CH and 

# update WhatsApp to the latest version
# make sure they have coverage
# Try again with “SALDO”. and let us know if it works or not. 

Knowing that they are indeed on the latest version of Whatsapp will help the Twilio engineers to further troubleshoot this. 

Please let me know how it goes
Thank you [~accountid:613e6eaa1238e8007108f513] . We tried to reach her again twice more today, with no luck, so we will close the case on our end, unless we hear from her again.
closing due to lack of response from CH
